					},
					"name": "Draco Heritage",
					"reference": "B77",
					"local_notes": "Your heritage as a Draco gives you unique capabilities and insight into the nature of your fire-related Arts. This grants a bonus to your IQ equal to this Advantage's level +1, and allows you to ignore prerequisites for many fire-related spells (GM discretion).",
