						},
						{
							"id": "mECH3X0f1Kj2kXfiF",
							"name": "Draco Arts",
							"local_notes": "While it takes some time, you can make the potency of your spells greater than most, and resist some level of Originium Arts dead zones due to it. Your heritage has led you to this point.",
